# 🌿 Canopy Web3 (Modular Smart Contracts)

A lightweight Web3 architecture inspired by Canopy:
- Sub-chain logic → CanopyStorage
- Shared security → CanopyStaking

## 🚀 Quick Start
npm install
npm run compile
npm run test

## 🌐 Deploy (Sepolia)
cp .env.example .env
# isi RPC_URL & PRIVATE_KEY
npm run deploy:sepolia

## 📦 Tech Stack
- Hardhat
- Ethers.js
- Solidity 0.8.x

